de.feu.showgo.model

Class ShowGo

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.feu.showgo.model.ShowGo

  • public class ShowGo
extends java.lang.Object
    This method is the root data store of the application. It contains a list of persons, theater plays, ensembles and productions. There should only be one instances of this class in the application, which is managed by the ShowGoDAO class.
